title: Vitamin C DILFS - EP9
description:
Hey Babe! is a podcast where comedians Chris Distefano and Sal Vulcano share stories and have fun. Let your hair down & come hang out with the BABES!


This episode the Babes talk Finding a new barber, haircut stress, dealing with the new social norms of the world post covid, Sal straightens his beard hair, Chris loves Sal’s fishermen look he’s got going, Don’t judge a book but it’s cover, Some men are on the gay fence it’s just what it is, Sal and Chris are often seen in a gay light, Sal talks hair health and products, a third of your life is spent in your bed, Sal loves a good pillow, A GOOD MATTRESS IS KEY TO LIFE, a story of two babes in Cincinnati, Sal is a DEEP sleeper, Chris fart tests his underware, Sal and Chris share the same favorite underware brand, the babes are addicted to athleisure, Sal has a candle addiction, disconnecting from social media is hard, real life is so much nicer than social media, sleep apnea is brutes, covid testing stories, do you sneeze into your mask?, Sal can predict when his body is getting sick, The babes have weak immune systems, Sal took so much vitamin c he crystalized his own urine, Sal doesn’t pee often, Sals doctor cut him off vitamin c, seltzer can take the place of a water, kidney stones are insane, Chris has a colonoscopy story, Sal talks about a prostate exam punishment from Impractical Jokers, its weird to say the word crap, Chris has some drama go down while he was at Disney World with his daughter and mother, dating apps during a pandemic is a dangerous place, Sal learns the truth about strawberries, Pears are the Staten Island of fruits, Chris gets pulled over for running a red light......HEY BABE! 


Rate us on iTunes! Follow us on social media @HeyBabePod
